fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.resource

Class PersistentResourceDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.resource.PersistentResourceDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Storable, PersistentResource, Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<PersistentEObject>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.resource.Resource, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.resource.Resource.Internal

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class PersistentResourceDecorator
extends Object
implements PersistentResource
    A PersistentResource wrapper that delegates all method calls to the decorated resource.

    This class can be extended by external tools to add behavior to an existing PersistentResource.

        Description copied from interface: PersistentResource

        Specified by:
        allInstancesOf in interface PersistentResource
        Parameters:
        eClass - the EClass for which look for instances
        strict - true if the lookup searches for strict instances
        Returns:
